name: LongActingMuscarinicAntagonistsLAMA
title: Long Acting Muscarinic Antagonists (LAMA)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: RxCUIs for inhaled short acting antimuscarinics),(Data Element Scope: DRUG_CLASS_MEMBERS: PHARMACOLOGIC:),(Inclusion Criteria: RxCUIs for inhalational agents that contain a long-acting muscarinic antagonist (LAMA) as an ingredient, either alone or in combination with other ingredients.),(Exclusion Criteria: Non-inhalational agents.)
